Package: UDID
Title: Universal Difference-in-Differences Estimator with Sensitivity Analysis
Version: 0.0.0
Authors@R: person("Chan", "Park", role = c("aut","cre"),
           email = "parkchan@illinois.com",
           comment = "Park & Tchetgen Tchetgen, 2025")
Description: Parametric and nonparametric universal difference-in-differences
    (UDID) estimators with sensitivity analysis. Includes efficient influence
    function based estimation, cross-fitting via Super Learner ensembles,
    and tools for sensitivity bounds and plotting.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
